svg.text: Contains details of fees and charges which are not associated with either Overdraft or features/benefits OtherFeesCharges

Type: string MinLength: 1 MaxLength: 350 Description: Name of the tariff
TariffName [0..1]

TariffType [0..1]

CappingPeriod [0..1]

FeeCapAmount [0..1]

Type: number Format: float Description: fee/charges are captured dependent on the number of occurrences rather than capped at a particular amount
FeeCapOccurrence [0..1]
